Description: =============
        Dremio client
        =============
        
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/dremio_client.svg
                :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/dremio_client
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/rymurr/dremio_client.svg
